1:1 COMMENT "# owned_protocol.z -- Owned protocol instance returned from a factory"
1:70 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "#"
2:2 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# `.create` is a self-contained constructor that heap-allocates its"
3:68 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# argument. The resulting protocol instance is escape-capable:"
4:63 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# it can be returned from a function, stored in a data structure,"
5:66 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# and passed around freely. Its destroy callback frees the heap data"
6:69 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "# when the protocol goes out of scope."
7:39 EOL "\n"
8:1 EOL "\n"
